  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b7c871f8520f3fc4ba9465f53662a56f, type: 3}
  m_Name: FirstGhost
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NPCData
  displayName: Ghost (?)
  lines:
  - You look like you've just seen a ghost!
  - Wait you can see me??
  - That's so awesome! I assume you're a security guard here. I've heard you guys
    have been getting some complaints.
  - Well... Since youre here and this is your job! I will admit we have been causing
    some mischeif.
  - Only because we need some help that only you humans can help with! It's hard
    communicating with you guys.
  - Many of us have some requests that we could use some help with. Just come talk
    to us!
  - Anyways, have a nice one! Hopefully you can help some of us out.
